      "span_text": "Teachers with greater levels of self-efficacy and greater outcome expectancy tend to prefer teaching science to other subjects (e.g. language, art) spend more time showing the most significant concepts to their children in practice, and generally feel confident about teaching science, answering children's questions and organizing activities as discussed by Lakshmanan, Heath, Perlmutter, & Elder [CITATION_1] ."
